  <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Orpheas Constantoyannis — Website Developer</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
</head>
<body>
<nav>
  <a href="#hero" class="logo">Orpheas Constantoyannis</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
    <li><a href="#process">Process</a></li>
    <li><a href="#tools">Tools</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section id="hero">
  <canvas id="hero-canvas"></canvas>
  <div class="hero-eyebrow"><span class="hero-dot"></span>Website Developer</div>
  <h1>Websites that work,<br><em>built with intelligence</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Clean, fast, modern websites — crafted by hand and accelerated by the best AI tools available.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="#services" class="btn-gold">See my services</a>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-outline">Let's talk</a>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="scene-divider"></div>

<section id="services">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">What I offer</p>
    <h2 class="reveal">Services</h2>
    <p class="section-intro reveal">Every project is different. I build websites by hand, using also AI — so you get quality work, faster.</p>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="card-shimmer"></div>
        <span class="svc-num">01</span>
        <h3>Website development</h3>
        <p>Custom-built sites — landing pages, portfolios, business sites — coded for speed and built to last.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="card-shimmer"></div>
       
        <span class="svc-num">02</span>
        <h3>Redesigns & rebuilds</h3>
        <p>Modernise an outdated site — cleaner design, faster load times, better results.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="card-shimmer"></div>
        <span class="svc-num">03</span>
        <h3>Ongoing maintenance</h3>
        <p>Monthly updates and fixes so your site stays fresh and secure without the stress.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="scene-divider"></div>

<section id="process">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">How I work</p>
    <h2 class="reveal">From brief to launch</h2>
    <p class="section-intro reveal">A simple, transparent process — no endless back-and-forth, no hidden surprises.</p>
    <div class="process-list">
      <div class="process-item">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <div><h3>Discovery call</h3><p>We talk through your goals, audience, and what success looks like. Thirty minutes, no pressure.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-item">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <div><h3>Proposal & plan</h3><p>A clear scope, timeline, and fixed price — so you know exactly what you're getting before we start.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-item">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <div><h3>Build & review</h3><p>I build and share progress at key milestones. You give feedback, I refine — collaboratively and efficiently.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-item">
        <div class="step-num">04</div>
        <div><h3>Launch & hand-off</h3><p>Your site goes live, fully tested. I walk you through everything and stay available for questions.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="scene-divider"></div>

<section id="tools">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">My toolkit</p>
    <h2 class="reveal">Tools I use</h2>
    <p class="section-intro reveal">Solid fundamentals paired with the best AI tools — building smarter without sacrificing quality.</p>
    <div class="tools-wrap reveal">
      <span class="tool-tag">HTML / CSS</span>
      <span class="tool-tag">JavaScript</span>
      <span class="tool-tag">React</span>
      <span class="tool-tag">Next.js</span>
      <span class="tool-tag">Tailwind CSS</span>
      <span class="tool-tag">Claude AI</span>
      <span class="tool-tag">ChatGPT</span>
      <span class="tool-tag">GitHub Copilot</span>
      <span class="tool-tag">Cursor</span>
      <span class="tool-tag">Vercel</span>
      <span class="tool-tag">Figma</span>
      <span class="tool-tag">Webflow</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
  <canvas id="contact-canvas"></canvas>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Ready to build something?</h2>
    <p>Tell me about your project and I'll get back to you within one business day.</p>
    <a href="mailto:hello@yoursite.com" class="btn-contact">Send me an email</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 Orpheas Constantoyannis · Built with code & AI</p>
</footer>

